    <Navbar />
    <div class="flex flex-col mt-[10vh]">
      <div class="hero">
        <h1
          class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl tracking-widest font-semibold before:content-['@']"
        >
          YuFan
        </h1>
        <div class="my-20 text-xl tracking-wide">
          <p class="mb-10">
            你好~我是來自台灣的網站開發人員，不論是前端還是後端，我都喜歡建立簡單且直觀的設計。!!!!!
          </p>
          <p>
            Hello! I'm a website developer from Taiwan. I enjoy creating simple
            and intuitive designs, whether it's on the front-end or back-end.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="projects">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-center tracking-wide my-10 font-semibold
        after:content-[' '] after:border-crusta-400 after:w-32 sm:after:w-40 after:mx-auto after:border-4 after:block after:mt-5 after:rounded"
        >
          Projects
        </h2>
        {
          projects.map((project) => (
            <ProjectCard
              title={project.title}
              image={project.image}
              content={project.content}
              tags={project.tags}
              url={project.url}
